# ============================================
# MCP SERVER API KEYS CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys
# Then add these to your system environment variables
# or source this file before running Claude Code
# ============================================

# --------------------------------------------
# SEARCH & RESEARCH
# --------------------------------------------

# Brave Search API - Company research, news, competitor monitoring
# Get free key (2,000 queries/month): https://brave.com/search/api
