# ============================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ============================================
#
# OPTION 1: Windows Environment Variables (Recommended)
# 1. Open System Properties > Environment Variables
# 2. Add each key as a User variable
# 3. Restart Claude Code
#
# OPTION 2: PowerShell Profile
# Add to $PROFILE:
#   $env:BRAVE_API_KEY = "your-key"
#   $env:EXA_API_KEY = "your-key"
#   etc.
#
# OPTION 3: Session-only (temporary)
# In PowerShell before starting Claude Code:
#   $env:BRAVE_API_KEY = "your-key"
#   claude
#
# ============================================
# PRIORITY ORDER (Get these first)
# ============================================
# 1. BRAVE_API_KEY - Free, instant, most useful for research
# 2. EXA_API_KEY - Superior company/people search
# 3. NOTION_API_KEY - Content calendar management
# 4. FIRECRAWL_API_KEY - Prospect website scraping
# 5. SLACK_BOT_TOKEN - Team notifications
# 6. TWITTER keys - Social media automation
